sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant REPL
    participant QueryEngine
    participant query as query.ts
    participant STE as StreamingToolExecutor
    participant API as Anthropic API
    participant Tool

    User->>REPL: Submit prompt
    REPL->>QueryEngine: yield* queryEngine(messages)

    Note over QueryEngine: Session-scoped AsyncGenerator
    QueryEngine->>query: yield* query(messages, options)

    Note over query: Turn-scoped loop
    query->>API: POST /messages (streaming)

    loop Streaming Response
        API-->>query: SSE chunks (text + tool_use)
        query-->>REPL: yield ProgressMessage

        alt Tool Use Detected
            query->>STE: executeTool(toolUse)

            Note over STE: Concurrent execution<br/>Read-write lock semantics
            STE->>Tool: tool.call(input)

            alt Permission Required
                Tool-->>REPL: Permission request
                REPL-->>User: Approve/Deny?
                User-->>REPL: Decision
                REPL-->>Tool: Permission result
            end

            Tool-->>STE: ToolResult
            STE-->>query: results[]

            Note over query: Append tool_result,<br/>loop back to API
            query->>API: POST /messages (with tool_result)
        end
    end

    query-->>QueryEngine: Final response
    QueryEngine-->>REPL: yield AssistantMessage
    REPL-->>User: Display response

    Note over QueryEngine: withRetry.ts wraps API calls<br/>629 lines, exponential backoff<br/>Clock skew detection
